OL,7,FA household that already charges its
OL,8,Felectric vehicle overnight using a
OL,9,Ftime-of-use tariff can save #332 a
OL,10,Fyear, the Department for Energy
OL,11,FSecurity and Net Zero (DESNZ) said.
OL,13,FThe plan would introduce requirements
OL,14,Ffor heat pumps to be sold "smart-
OL,15,Fready", in line with regulations that
OL,16,Falready apply to electric vehicle
OL,17,Fchargers.
