OL,5,Chouseholds money
OL,7,FThis would give heat pump owners the
OL,8,Fchoice to activate smart functionality
OL,9,Fand make savings by heating their
OL,10,Fhomes when energy is cheaper, saving
OL,11,Faround #100 per year compared with the
OL,12,Fcost of a gas boiler.
OL,14,FA range of appliances including
OL,15,Felectric vehicle smart charge points,
OL,16,Fheat pumps and battery energy storage
OL,17,Fsystems will have to be able to
OL,18,Foperate across different tariffs,
OL,19,Fmeaning they are not tied to one
OL,20,Fenergy supplier and consumers are not
OL,21,Flocked into one plan.
