OL,4,Cfunction under plans to save
OL,5,Chouseholds money
OL,7,FThe new regulations for heat devices
OL,8,Fwould apply to hydronic heat pumps,
OL,9,Fstorage heaters, heat batteries,
OL,10,Fstandalone direct electric hot water
OL,11,Fcylinders, hot water heat pumps and
OL,12,Fhybrid heat pumps, all up to a thermal
OL,13,Fcapacity of 45kW.
OL,15,FThe Government said it planned to put
OL,16,Fforward secondary legislation on
OL,17,Fenergy smart appliances within the
OL,18,Fnext year.
