OL,7,FThere would then be a 20-month period
OL,8,Fto allow manufacturers to update
OL,9,Fproduction, before the regulations
OL,10,Fwill be enforced.
OL,12,FConsumers would always retain the
OL,13,Foption to use their devices in non-
OL,14,Fsmart mode, the DESNZ said.
OL,16,FEnergy minister Michael Shanks said:
OL,17,F"From EV chargers to heat pumps, smart
OL,18,Fappliances can do the hard work for
OL,19,Fconsumers by automatically using
OL,20,Fenergy when the price is low.
