OL,7,F"We want to put more money in people's
OL,8,Fpockets as part of our Plan for Change
OL,9,Fby making it easier for people to
OL,10,Fbenefit from cheaper off-peak tariffs
OL,11,Fin their home.
OL,13,F"These new standards will also bring a
OL,14,Fcommon sense approach to smart
OL,15,Fappliances by ensuring different
OL,16,Fbrands and models can operate across
OL,17,Fdifferent energy suppliers, allowing
OL,18,Fconsumers to shop around for the best
OL,19,Fdeals."
